assen und ihr in der familienpolitischen Diskussion einen größeren Stellenwert einzuräumen. Als Gesellschaft und als Bürger haben wir allen Grund, uns für Eltern zu interessieren – den Kindern zuliebe.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aParenting. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh  aErziehung.  aLebenssituation.  aSituation der Eltern.1 aBorchard, Michael, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHenry-Huthmacher, Christine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHenry-Huthmacher, Christine, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMerkle, Tanja, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWippermann, Carsten, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aWippermann, Carsten, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Social Sciences 2000 - 2014z9783110638080oZDB-23-GSS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket Best of Lucius & Luciusz97831105150770 cprintz978382820424940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978382826009240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783828260092423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783828260092/original  a978-3-11-051507-7  eBook-Paket Best of Lucius & Lucius  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GSSc2000d2014